<h4 id="set-range-of-bits">Set range of bits</h4>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><figcaption class='code-header'><span>Set range</span>  <a href='https://gist.github.com/coolgoose85/458a1f67d61f8def1120' target='_blank'>Range Unset Mask </a></figcaption> <div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre>
This mask is similar to Range Unset Mask created earlier with an <span style="color:#F00;background-color:#FAA">‘</span>exception<span style="color:#F00;background-color:#FAA">’</span>
in last&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;/&lt;strong&gt;**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;***
<span style="color:#777">//In “Range UNset Mask” we created following</span>
<span style="color:#777">//For e.g. 1001 1001</span>
<span style="color:#777">//Unset bits from 2 to 5 i.e. 1 0 0 1 1 0 0 1 =&amp;gt; 10 0000 01</span>
<span style="color:#777">//                               |- - - -| </span>
<span style="color:#777">//                      Bits  7 6 5 4 3 2 1 0  &lt;br /&gt;</span>
<span style="color:#777">//Step1</span>
<span style="color:#777">//——</span>
<span style="color:#777">//To unset range of bits we need to create MASK</span>
<span style="color:#777">// val  = 1001 1001</span>
<span style="color:#777">// Mask = 1100 0011 (AND)</span>
<span style="color:#777">//      _____________</span>
<span style="color:#777">//        1000 0001</span>
**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**&lt;/strong&gt;*/&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We will be creating the same mask in addition we will 
TOGGLE the bits of <span style="color:#F00;background-color:#FAA">“</span>unset mask<span style="color:#F00;background-color:#FAA">”</span>&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Unset MASK = <span style="color:#00D">1100</span> <span style="color:#40E">0011</span>
 TOGGLE     = <span style="color:#40E">0011</span> <span style="color:#00D">1100</span>    ~(Unset Mask)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now perform OR will val
 val  = <span style="color:#00D">1001</span> <span style="color:#00D">1001</span>
 Mask = <span style="color:#40E">0011</span> <span style="color:#00D">1100</span> (OR)
      &lt;strong&gt;__&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;__&lt;/strong&gt;_
